<br>
A little RTA (the ezboard) history.<br>
<br>
It was created by Sareliel, Rewena, Edwina, Braden, Jerrica and a few others.  Who are they?  They were some of the leaders of the guilds who, at the time, were the Uber Guilds of the Rathe.<br>
<br>
They created this board to have &quot;private conversations&quot; about VS and Trakenon.  When others found this board, and started added their 2cp to the discussion, they let them, but put the Rotation Agreement Discussion in a Password Protected Forum that lasted up to a few years ago.  Even after the original founders of this board left the game, or moved to Zeb, their Legacy lived on.<br>
<br>
This board was <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>never</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> the &quot;property&quot; of the people of the Rathe.  It was created as a means for folks from different high-end (at the time) guilds to come and discuss matters pertaining to them, in neutral territory.<br>
<br>
That's all it is now, neutral territory.<br>
<br>
The &quot;Private Discussions&quot; that you so abhor have a precedent set from the dim past of this board, so the Elemental Forum is in keeping with the original concept of this Board. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=trivilusbotsrep>TrivilusBotSrep</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>BotS - Rep</span><br>  Posts: 78<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(8/20/03 4:33 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Elemental planes forum</span><hr size=1> I cant believe that Roggulbuk isnt a trustworthy enough person for you Rigg. Not only is he impartial and fair but hell he's your Guild Leader isnt he? <br>
