Nyca,<br>
Your history is a bit off.  The RTA was founded to be a central location where the big guilds of the time (BotS, KEG, CiW) could post thier intent to raid Fear.  Instead of having to post messages on all the other guilds forums, Sareliel created the Rathe Travel Agency (traveling in the only extra-planar raid zones at that time).  Several months went by and they developed the Calendar system.  It wasn't until quite some time later that BotS and KEG formed the Trakanon rotation.<br>
<br>
The RTA is not Flame Central (even if it does get the most posts), the RTA is not the General forum.  The RTA is the Guild Representatives Forum, and any other forums that are required to work out how to share the content on this server.  The RTA is supposed to be the common middle ground that people can come to discuss issues revolving the rotations and reservation systems.<br>
