<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The RTA has evolved quite a bit over time. From simply a site where 3 guilds posts thier intent to raid a zone, to a calendar system, to the advent of rotations, to multi-day/mulit-mob rotations, and more.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Bells and whistles.  All I see is bells and whistles.<br>
