<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The RTA has evolved quite a bit over time. From simply a site where 3 guilds posts thier intent to raid a zone (to 4 guilds who control all of the raid content), to a calendar system (controlled by you), to the advent of rotations (controlled by you), to multi-day/mulit-mob rotations (controlled by you), and more (ditto).<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
