<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>On one last final note, just because we disagree with you does not give you the right to insult us by calling us idiots, elitists, monkeys or anything else you think of at the time. If that is the level of &quot;debate&quot; you are looking for, I'll move this to the Flame Central and point Borick to it, then ignore it like most of the other trash there.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->I don't know that I've ever called you an 'idiot' persay, but it is no more fitting for you to 'assume' that we lack the intelligence to comprehend your exhalted level of greatness ...elitist?, yes, when the shoe fits I suppose ...monkeys? No, that was a damn funny example, though.  Perhaps it hit a little close to home for you, Milambus?<br>
